Package com.saguaro.entity

Class GroceryItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.saguaro.entity.GroceryItem
  • @Entity
public class GroceryItem
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements a grocery item entity, and is used by Hibernate to generate a corresponding database representation.

    Grocery items are contained within grocery lists, however grocery items are shared in between lists. This means that two lists containing an item with the same name will have pointers to the same item object.

    Author:
    Charles Wong
